rows.label: qev060901_MSG0001
rows.name:
Hmm? Oh! You're the human who helped me earlier!
You could not have come at a better time. *fsssh*[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev060901_MSG0002
rows.name:
What, you're together with this jewel thief? Ha!
Guess I'll put the BOTH of you behind bars![ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev060901_MSG0003
rows.name:
So...yes. I assume that paints a fairly clear picture of
my present conundrum. *fsssh* This BLADE is treating
me like a criminal for no reason at all.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev060901_MSG0004
rows.name:
*fsssh* To a Zaruboggan, jewels are just colorful dirt.
Why would I steal something of no value to me?[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev060901_JNK0010
rows.name: Sympathize

rows.label: qev060901_SEL0011
rows.name:
Tell Shiraton that you're sorry
he's being put through all this.

rows.label: qev060901_JNK0020
rows.name: Doubt

rows.label: qev060901_SEL0021
rows.name: Ask Shiraton if he really doesn't find jewels beautiful.

rows.label: qev060901_MSG0005
rows.name: *fsssh* If only all humans were so understanding.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev060901_MSG0006
rows.name:
Much as it pains me to drag you into this, do you
think you might help me? You're the only one I can
turn to. *fsssh*[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev060901_MSG0007
rows.name:
*fsssh* Honestly, I find the glinting and flashing
unsettling. I can't understand why humans delight so
in wearing such things.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev060901_MSG0008
rows.name:
I can state with absolute certainty that I have not and
would not steal jewels. *fsssh* So much as it pains me
to ask, do you think you might help me?[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev060901_MSG0009
rows.name:
You are the only one in this foreign city I can turn to.
*fsssh*[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev060901_MSG0010
rows.name:
Thank you. *fsssh* First, I would ask that you try talking
to the BLADE officer here.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev060901_MSG0013
rows.name:
I was passing through, collecting voltant, when this
woman suddenly assaulted me with accusations. *fsssh*[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev060901_MSG0014
rows.name:
I swear I have not stolen any jewels. *fsssh*
Please help me to prove my innocence.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev060901_MSG0015
rows.name:
*fsssh* That car that left from the east exit seemed to be
in quite the hurry. Suspiciously so, I think.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev060901_MSG0055
rows.name:
Factoring for its current velocity, it could be at the
East Janpath Plain by now. *fsssh*[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev060901_MSG0016
rows.name: Please find the culprit and prove my innocence. *fsssh*[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev060901_MSG0019
rows.name: Well. *fsssh* I expect this resolves the matter?[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev060901_MSG0020
rows.name:
Thank you so very much for your help. *fsssh*
Please take this for your trouble.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev060901_MSG0021
rows.name:
And now, I have a collection route to get back to.
New LA still has mountains of voltant waiting to be
claimed! *fsssh*[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev060901_MSG0022
rows.name: Um...[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev060901_MSG0023
rows.name:
Listen, I'm sorry. It was wrong of me to judge you by
the way you look.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev060901_MSG0024
rows.name:
*fsssh* As long as I can get back to work, I am
content. You were simply doing your own job.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev060901_MSG0025
rows.name:
If anything, let this mishap ensure you do not make the
same error in the future. Live and learn, yes? *fsssh*[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev060901_MSG0026
rows.name:
...Are all his kind that nice? I just treated him like a
total criminal because of his appearance.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev060901_MSG0027
rows.name: Ugh, I'm just so...STUPID![ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev060901_JNK0030
rows.name: Comfort

rows.label: qev060901_SEL0031
rows.name: Tell Tracey that mistakes lead to growth.

rows.label: qev060901_JNK0040
rows.name: Blame

rows.label: qev060901_SEL0041
rows.name: Tell Tracey to never make baseless accusations again.

rows.label: qev060901_MSG0028
rows.name: Heh. You're pretty nice too.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev060901_MSG0029
rows.name:
Today I learned that a detective's instincts are no
substitute for evidence. It's a lesson I won't forget.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev060901_MSG0030
rows.name: Next time, I'll rely on my woman's instinct all the way![ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev060901_MSG0031
rows.name:
All right! As of this moment, I'm a new woman!
Anybody who looks like they're making trouble for my
Zaruboggan friends is getting arrested![ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev060901_MSG0032
rows.name: You're right. Thanks for being blunt with me.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev060901_MSG0033
rows.name:
I've learned something really important hereâ€”
a detective's instincts are no substitute for evidence.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev060901_MSG0034
rows.name: Next time, I'll rely on my woman's instinct all the way![ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev060901_MSG0035
rows.name:
All right! As of this moment, I'm a new woman!
Anybody who looks like they're making trouble for my
Zaruboggan friends is getting arrested![ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev060901_MSG0017
rows.name:
*fsssh* Since even you have betrayed me, if this doesn't
work, I'll resign myself to whatever fate may come.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev060901_MSG0018
rows.name:
But please at least investigate the car that left through
the east gate. *fsssh*[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev060901_MSG0056
rows.name:
Factoring for its current velocity, it could be at the
East Janpath Plain by now. *fsssh*[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev060901_MSG0036
rows.name: Whew... *fsssh* I expect this resolves the matter?[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev060901_MSG0037
rows.name:
You may have treated me like a common criminal for
a while, but in the end you came to my aid. *fsssh*.
You have my thanks for that.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev060901_MSG0038
rows.name: *fsssh* Here is something for your troubles.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev060901_JNK0050
rows.name: Comfort

rows.label: qev060901_SEL0051
rows.name: Tell Tracey that mistakes lead to growth.

rows.label: qev060901_JNK0060
rows.name: Blame

rows.label: qev060901_SEL0061
rows.name: Tell Tracey to never to make baseless accusations again.

rows.label: qev060901_MSG0046
rows.name:
Heh. I guess we're together in that, huh? We'll have to
make sure we don't go making the same one again.[ST:wait ]

substitute for evidence. It's a lesson I won't forget.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev060901_MSG0050
rows.name: But...you agreed with me for a while there...[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev060901_MSG0051
rows.name:
No, yeah, you're right. That's no excuse.
I have to learn from examples good and bad.[ST:wait ]
